# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok britain 's former world rally champion richard burns has left hospital as he continues his brave fight against a brain tumor .
# ::alignments
(l / leave-11
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Richard"
                  :op2 "Burn")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "Kingdom"))
                  :ARG2 (c2 / champion
                        :mod (r / rally-01
                              :mod (w / world)))
                  :time (f / former)))
      :ARG1 (h2 / hospital)
      :time (c3 / continue-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (f2 / fight-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (t / tumor
                        :mod (b / brain))
                  :ARG0-of (b2 / brave-02))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok rival palestinian factions hamas and fatah were set to hold talks here monday on forming a unity government after reportedly reaching agreement the day before on creating a joint security force in gaza .
# ::alignments
(s / set-08
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Hamas"))
            :op2 (p2 / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Fatah"))
            :ARG0-of (r / rival-01
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Palestine"))))
      :ARG2 (h / hold-04
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (t / talk-01
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (f / form-01
                        :ARG0 a
                        :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01)
                              :mod (u / unity))))
            :location (h2 / here)
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (m / monday)))
      :time (a2 / after
            :op1 (r2 / reach-01
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (a3 / agree-01
                        :ARG1 (c2 / create-01
                              :ARG1 (f2 / force
                                    :mod (s2 / security)
                                    :mod (j / joint))
                              :location (c3 / city
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Gaza"))))
                  :ARG1-of (r3 / report-01)
                  :time (b / before
                        :op1 h
                        :quant (t2 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (d2 / day))))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :mod (f / federal))

                  :ARG0-of (f2 / farm-01
                        :ARG1 (t2 / tobacco)))
            :ARG1 p
            :condition (t3 / threaten-01
                  :ARG0 (c / company
                        :mod (c2 / cigarette))
                  :ARG1 (c3 / contract
                        :mod (s / sell-01)))
            :ARG1-of (c4 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (s2 / sue-02
                        :ARG2 (a / allege-01
                              :ARG1 (c5 / conspire-01
                                    :ARG1 (f3 / fix-02
                                          :ARG1 (p3 / price)))))))
      :ARG2 p2)
